                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9965" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1488</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2172 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从垃圾食品到绿色名片： 麻辣王子品牌重塑赋能产业链韧性</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Junk Food to Green Business Card: Malawangzi&#39;s Brand Reinvention Empowers Industrial Chain Resilience</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘婷，罗芳雪，占永谦，蒋亦涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南麻辣王子食品有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麻辣王子；品牌重塑；产业链韧性；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Spicy Prince; brand reshaping; industrial chain resilience</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，传统产业链面临发展受制等突出问题，在复杂动态环境下，如何推进传统企业品牌重塑并赋能产业链韧性提升，成为传统企业发展必须破解的共同课题。本案例聚焦湖南麻辣王子食品有限公司（以下简称“麻辣王子”）以品牌重塑赋能产业链韧性的发展历程，全方位展现这家辣条制造企业如何实现从“垃圾食品”到“绿色名片”的价值跃升，最终推动辣条产业链韧性的系统性提升。案例以麻辣王子“麻辣基因的觉醒与品类重构—视觉革新与传播破圈—辣条集群的韧性生长”为主线，深入解析其品牌重塑的核心逻辑及赋能产业链韧性的作用机制，旨在为传统企业转型发展与传统产业链韧性提升提供可借鉴的路径参考，助力业界理解品牌重塑内涵、把握产业链协同发展的关键要素。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, traditional industrial chains have faced prominent issues such as restricted development. In a complex and dynamic environment, how to promote brand reinvention of traditional enterprises and empower the enhancement of industrial chain resilience has become a common challenge that must be addressed for the development of traditional enterprises. This case focuses on the development journey of Hunan Malawangzi Food Co., Ltd. (&quot;Malawangzi&quot; for short) in empowering industrial chain resilience through brand reinvention, comprehensively demonstrating how this spicy strip manufacturing enterprise has achieved a value leap from &quot;junk food&quot; to a &quot;green business card,&quot; ultimately driving the systematic enhancement of the spicy strip industrial chain&#39;s resilience. Taking Malawangzi&#39;s main line of &quot;Awakening of Spicy Genes and Category Reconstruction—Visual Innovation and Communication Breakthrough—Resilient Growth of Spicy Strip Clusters,&quot; the case deeply analyzes the core logic of its brand reinvention and the mechanism of empowering industrial chain resilience. It aims to provide referenceable paths for the transformation and development of traditional enterprises and the enhancement of traditional industrial chain resilience, helping the industry understand the connotation of brand reinvention and grasp the key elements of industrial chain collaborative development.
Keywords:Malawangzi; Brand Reinvention; Industrial Chain Resilience</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《品牌管理》、《市场营销》、《战略管理》、《产业链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业链韧性；品牌重塑</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
